y the linearized Einstein's equations, which\nare shown to be equivalent to the holographic first law of complexity, thereby\nadvocating for a principle of 'spacetime complexity'. Lastly, we argue\nLorentzian threads provide a notion of emergent time. This article is an\nexpanded and detailed version of [arXiv:2105.12735], including several new\nresults.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Jun 2021 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Jan 2022 11:16:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 14 Feb 2022 18:44:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-02"}
