 system dynamics to limit cycle\noscillations and thus provide an early warning signal for the onset of\nthermoacoustic instability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Jun 2021 03:55:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Aug 2021 11:49:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-16"}
