tion luminosity that is realized\nwhen the accretion rate of the disk onto the BH is consistent with that via the\nHoyle-Lyttleton mechanism taking into account the effect of radiation. This\nimplies the intermediate-mass black holes moving in the dense dusty-gas are\nidentified as luminous objects in the infrared band.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Jun 2021 10:01:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-25"}
