the Gaussian fixed point is missing in the\nRG flow with the constant term. Finally, comments on the application of our\nresults to cosmological models are provided.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Jun 2021 11:34:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 31 Mar 2022 08:51:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-01"}
